public abstract class TestBaseFixture<RE extends IRingElement<RE>>
extends java.lang.Object
implements TestBaseInterface<RE>

This class encapsulates the fixture for the factory used to create instances of the base type and a LinAlgFactory instance.

Furthermore, it provides convenience methods to examine the annotations of the class of the factory provided by TestBaseInterface.getFactory().
